<h1 class='property-title'>background-origin</h1>
<p class='property-description'>The<code> background-origin </code>CSS property determines the background positioning area, that is the position of the origin of an image specified using the <code><a rel="custom" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/CSS/background-image">background-image</a></code>
 CSS property.</p>